    <string name="about_title">About &amp; Privacy</string>
    <string name="about_body">Unlock Capture creates photos or short videos with the front camera when specific events are detected, such as failed or successful unlock attempts.\n\nRecording runs through a foreground service, so Android shows a visible notification while it is active.\n\nStorage locations:\n• Photos: Pictures/UnlockCapture\n• Videos: Movies/UnlockCapture\n\nNote: This app is intended for your own devices and requires the device owner’s consent.</string>

